categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: During the last millennium of the Galactic Republic a female individual served within the Jedi Order as a Jedi Knight, specializing as a Jedi Consular. In 181 BBY, the Knight and her Padawan were dispatched to bring a resolution to the Dark Jedi Conflict, a war that had been initiated in 188 BBY when the Dark Jedi Kibh Jeen and his pirate army had declared war on the inhabitants of the Cularin system. The two Jedi forged the system's population into an effective fighting force and lured Jeen's army into a trap. During a fiercely-fought space battle, the pirates were defeated and the two Jedi confronted and killed Jeen.
